{"id": "art-251", "label": "Art. 251", "title": "Art. 251", "slug": "art-251", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 251 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_91200097\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1733\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_91200097\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Nulitatea unei fuziuni sau diviz&#259;ri poate fi\ndeclarat&#259; numai prin hot&#259;râre judec&#259;toreasc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1925415480\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1732\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1925415480\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)De la data realiz&#259;rii sale, potrivit art. 249,\nfuziunea, respectiv divizarea poate fi declarat&#259; nul&#259; doar dac&#259;\nnu a fost supus&#259; unui control de legalitate sau dac&#259; hot&#259;rârea\nuneia dintre adun&#259;rile generale care au votat proiectul fuziunii sau al\ndiviz&#259;rii este nul&#259; ori anulabil&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_238449429\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1731\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_238449429\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Procedurile de anulare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> fuziunii sau\ndiviz&#259;rii nu pot fi <span class=SpellE>ini&#355;iate</span> dup&#259;\nexpirarea unui termen de 6 luni de la data la care fuziunea sau divizarea a\ndevenit efectiv&#259;, în temeiul art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>249</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, sau dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> a\nfost rectificat&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_910342008\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1730\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_910342008\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dac&#259; neregularitatea ce poate conduce la declararea\n<span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> unei fuziuni sau diviz&#259;ri\npoate fi remediat&#259;, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\ncompetent&#259; acord&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nimplicate un termen pentru rectificarea acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_442206712\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1729\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_442206712\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Hot&#259;rârea definitiv&#259; de declarare a <span\nclass=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> unei fuziuni sau diviz&#259;ri va fi\nînaintat&#259; din oficiu de c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;&#259;</span>\noficiilor registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> de la sediile <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> implicate în fuziunea sau divizarea\nrespectiv&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1465950372\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1728\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1465950372\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Hot&#259;rârea definitiv&#259; de declarare a <span\nclass=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> unei fuziuni ori diviz&#259;ri nu aduce\natingere prin ea <span class=SpellE>îns&#259;&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>valabilit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> n&#259;scute în sarcina sau în\nbeneficiul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante ori <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> beneficiare, angajate dup&#259; ce\nfuziunea sau divizarea au devenit efective, în temeiul art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>249</span><span style='color:black'>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nînainte ca hot&#259;rârea de declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ns&#259; fie publicat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2002912726\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1727\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2002912726\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)În cazul declar&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nunei fuziuni, <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> participante la\nfuziunea respectiv&#259; r&#259;spund solidar pentru <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante, angajate în perioada\n<span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionat&#259;</span> la alin. (6).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_358944359\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1726\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_358944359\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)În cazul declar&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nunei diviz&#259;ri, fiecare dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare r&#259;spunde pentru propriile <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>,\nangajate în perioada prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (6). Societatea divizat&#259;\nr&#259;spunde, de asemenea, pentru aceste <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>,\nîn limita cotei de active nete transferate <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nbeneficiare în contul c&#259;reia au luat <span class=SpellE>na&#351;tere</span>\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> respective.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}